name: Shvpeshifter Jiu Jitsu
description: Decentralizing Jiu Jitsu, promoting peaceful parenting, the least interesting-yet-interesting part of Jiu Jitsu is the fighting
payDisclosure: We minted the first Brazilian Jiu Jitsu belts as NFTs on Ethereum - to bridge awareness of NFTs with a simple, real-world example. Now, we want to bring the practice of Jiu Jitsu to the rest of the world. Perhaps reducing violence is not done through podcasting and audiobooks - instead, let us contain violence - in both meanings of the world 'contain.'
